OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FThe alleged getaway driver in an
OL,8,Fattack on an Iranian journalist in
OL,9,FLondon said it was a "big surprise"
OL,10,Fwhen two men he drove from the scene
OL,11,Fsaid there had been a stabbing, a jury
OL,12,Fhas heard.
OL,14,FIran International journalist Pouria
OL,15,FZeraati was left bleeding in the
OL,16,Fstreet after he was attacked by
OL,17,Fproxies of the Iranian regime in
OL,18,FWimbledon, south-west London, on March
OL,19,F29 2024, Woolwich Crown Court has
OL,20,Fheard.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
