FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FRomanian nationals Nandito Badea, 21,
OL,8,Fand George Stana, 25, have both
OL,9,Fpleaded not guilty to charges of
OL,10,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,11,Fbodily harm and wounding.
OL,13,FStana was waiting in a blue Mazda 3,
OL,14,Fbelieving that a robbery and not a
OL,15,Fstabbing would take place, the court
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,18,FUnder cross-examination, prosecutor
OL,19,FDuncan Atkinson KC said: "Did you ask
OL,20,Fany questions about who you were going
OL,21,Fto rob?
OL,26,@{D@ZOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,F"The plan was to approach this man,
OL,8,Fslap him a few times to tell him to
OL,9,Fstop sleeping with someone's wife and
OL,10,Ftake his watch?"
OL,12,FStana replied: "Yes."
OL,14,FStana said he did not see any of them
OL,15,Fcarry knives or "knew why they would
OL,16,Fhave knives".
OL,18,FMr Atkinson suggested to Stana: "It
OL,19,Fwas no surprise to you when they came
OL,20,Fto the car and talked of having cut
OL,21,Fhim?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@PO]tD@POUtD@UO]wD@QOUxD@LO]zD@
OL,26,AaOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FStana responded: "Believe me, it was a
OL,8,Fbig surprise."
OL,10,FStana said he drove the two men
OL,11,Fquickly from the scene, telling the
OL,12,Fcourt it would be "normal to leave
OL,13,Fquickly if you go to rob someone ` how
OL,14,Fwould you behave?"
OL,16,FHe denied that a series of calls after
OL,17,Fthe incident was part of the plot to
OL,18,Fhelp them flee the country.
OL,20,FHe said: "We had no arrangement.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@NO]tD@SOUvD@RO]|D@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,F"We just left because of the stabbing,
OL,8,Fbut if the stabbing had not happened,
OL,9,Fwe would not have left."
OL,11,FMr Atkinson told Stana: "When you came
OL,12,Fto this country in February 2023, it
OL,13,Fwas with the view to attacking Mr
OL,14,FZeraati?
OL,16,F"And when you went to Queensmere Road
OL,17,Fa year later, you were part of a plan
OL,18,Fto do the same thing?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@XO]sD@YOUxD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FStana denied this was true before Mr
OL,8,FAtkinson suggested that in 2024, he
OL,9,Fwent "with two others to do the dirty
OL,10,Fwork on that occasion" and they were
OL,11,F"acting as a team when you were there".
OL,13,FStana insisted this description of
OL,14,Fevents was "not true", adding: "This
OL,15,Fjust happened. I personally did not
OL,16,Fwant that man to be stabbed."
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@VO]sD@AOUsD@fO]vD@LOUvD@UO]vD@
OL,26,A`OUxD@]O]
