OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FIt is alleged that the defendants
OL,8,Facted as a team to carry out the
OL,9,Fattack with another man ` named as
OL,10,FDavid Andrei, who is not a defendant
OL,11,Fin the trial ` with Stana acting as
OL,12,Fthe getaway driver.
OL,14,FThe journalist was attacked by two men
OL,15,Fas he walked to his car in Queensmere
OL,16,FRoad and was stabbed in the thigh.
OL,18,FJurors have been told the defendants
OL,19,Fheaded to Heathrow Airport on the day
OL,20,Fof the alleged attack and fled to
OL,21,FGeneva in Switzerland.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
