PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780409469
OL,3,CAccused getaway driver says stabbing
OL,4,Cof Iranian journalist was a 'big
OL,5,Csurprise'
OL,7,FThe court has heard they ordered a
OL,8,Ftaxi using the Bolt app, initially
OL,9,Fsetting the drop-off location as
OL,10,FTottenham, then adjusting it to Luton,
OL,11,Fand finally Heathrow Airport.
OL,13,FMr Zeraati worked for Iran
OL,14,FInternational, a competitor of the
OL,15,Fstate broadcaster, which the Iranian
OL,16,Fregime designated as a terrorist
OL,17,Forganisation and branded "a network of
OL,18,Fspies", the court has heard.
OL,26,@yD@ZOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
